org.safs.selenium.webdriver.lib

Class RemoteDriver.SessionInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.safs.selenium.webdriver.lib.RemoteDriver.SessionInfo
  • Enclosing class:
    RemoteDriver

    public static class RemoteDriver.SessionInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains information for reconnecting a session.
    The session info string contains some fields separated by RemoteDriver.SPLITTER
    The current format of the session info string is as below:

    ID=serverHost_SP_sessionid_SP_browserName_SP_browserVersion_SP_platform_SP_commandCodecClassName_SP_responseCodecClassName_SP_<extraParameters>
    <extraParameters> are optional parameter as below

    • firefoxProfile
    • chromeUserDataDir
    • chromeProfileDir
    • chromePreference
    • chromeExcludeOptions
    • firefoxPreference
    • networkConditions
    • customCapabilites
